# warp-split.list — prefixes to route via WARP (listed = out-warp, unlisted = eth0).
#
# FORMAT
#   One IPv4 CIDR per line. Blank lines and # comments are ignored.
#   Use broad provider ranges, NOT individual /32s: Telegram, Google, and similar
#   CDNs round-robin across thousands of IPs; a hand-picked /32 will miss most of
#   them. A /32 for a stable single-IP endpoint is fine.
#
# ENDPOINT EXCLUSION
#   Do NOT add 162.159.195.1/32 (the WARP endpoint itself) — vpnbot-warp-split
#   always installs an explicit /32 route for the endpoint via eth0 in the routing
#   table, regardless of what is listed here. Adding it here would be a no-op.
#
# APPLYING CHANGES
#   After editing the live list restart the service to re-apply:
#     systemctl restart vpnbot-warp-split
#   Verify: ip route show table <T>   (T = fwmark from `awg show out-warp fwmark`)

# ── Telegram ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Core DC address ranges (authoritative allocation, stable)
91.108.4.0/22
91.108.8.0/22
91.108.12.0/22
91.108.16.0/22
91.108.20.0/22
91.108.56.0/22
149.154.160.0/20
# CDN and media delivery (Cloudflare-hosted Telegram assets)
91.105.192.0/23
95.161.64.0/20

# ── Google ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Broad Google/GCP announced ranges — cover Search, YouTube, Drive, Meet, etc.
# Narrow /32 picks will miss round-robin; prefer /16 or wider.
142.250.0.0/15
172.217.0.0/16
216.58.192.0/19
35.190.0.0/15
34.64.0.0/10
8.8.8.0/24
8.8.4.0/24

# ── GitHub ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
185.199.108.0/22
140.82.112.0/20
192.30.252.0/22

# ── Cloudflare ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Cloudflare CDN (1.1.1.1 DNS, Workers, Pages, broad CDN traffic).
# Note: the WARP endpoint 162.159.195.1 lives inside 162.159.192.0/22 —
# vpnbot-warp-split pins it to eth0 via an anti-loop /32, so including the
# broader block here is safe and routes the rest via WARP.
104.16.0.0/12
162.158.0.0/15
162.159.0.0/16
172.64.0.0/13
